description: A world of taste for the explorer in you! The Explorers Club is taking it's years of experience and skill to the streets to bring everyone a little taste of the world. With an eclectic menu and a strong Cuban influence, the Explorers club has something for everyone. Meat-eaters, vegetarians, vegans? The Explorers Club Food Truck is ready and waiting for you!
name: Explorers Club Food Truck
